            <h2>What is Movie Tracker?</h2>
            <p>Movie Tracker is a web application designed to help movie enthusiasts like you keep track of the movies you've watched, rate them, and share your reviews with others. Whether you're a casual viewer or a serious cinephile, Movie Tracker makes it easy to organize your movie-watching journey.</p>

            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Movie Search:</strong> Find movies from an extensive database with detailed information.</li>
                <li><strong>Track Your Movies:</strong> Add movies to your profile and create your personal movie collection.</li>
                <li><strong>Ratings & Reviews:</strong> Rate movies and leave reviews for others to read.</li>
                <li><strong>Personalized Recommendations:</strong> Coming soon, you will receive personalized recommendations based on your watch history.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Future Plans</h2>
            <p>We're always looking to improve and grow Movie Tracker. Here's what's coming soon:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Watchlist:</strong> Create a list of movies you want to watch in the future.</li>
                <li><strong>Friend Connections:</strong> Follow your friends to see what they are watching and their ratings.</li>
                <li><strong>Mobile App:</strong> A mobile version of Movie Tracker to take your movie collection on the go!</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Get Involved</h2>
            <p>If you have suggestions or want to stay updated on our latest features, be sure to follow us on social media or sign up for our newsletter!</p>
        </div>
